      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;r-package-for-generating-publication-websites-based-on-hugo-theme-academic&#34;&gt;R Package For Generating (Publication) Websites Based on Hugo Theme Academic&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using the following tools:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt;: static website generator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://sourcethemes.com/academic/&#34;&gt;Academic&lt;/a&gt;: a open-source theme for &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; adapted to the needs of researchers and/or small research labs. For example used by Stanford`s Causality in Cognition Lab (see: &lt;a href=&#34;https://cicl.stanford.edu&#34;&gt;https://cicl.stanford.edu&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;R package &lt;a href=&#34;https://bookdown.org/yihui/blogdown&#34;&gt;blogdown&lt;/a&gt;: for generating the website from R(Studio) and&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://bookdown.org/yihui/blogdown/github-pages.html&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=&#34;https://bookdown.org/yihui/blogdown/gitlab-pages.html&#34;&gt;GitLab&lt;/a&gt; Pages: for automatically deploying the website for free&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
